description: This Chainlink VRF top 1% rating Parvati purrs with a rating of 95, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 190, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
